body:
**🍋 Welcome to Lemon Power , a create mod addon focusing on lemon of course but also new way of automating blaze burner fuel, lemonade, and much more! 🍋**
Dependence : Create mod, Create: Craft & Additions

My advice is to play this mod with Jei for the craft or else you'll be confused.

adds :

- Lemon : used to make all the mod's component, can be eaten;
- Bolted lemon : useless for now but it is planned to use it as a battery;
- Lemonade + Lemonade Mocktail : Two drinks made from lemon juice and a mixture of lemon juice and syrup;
- Lemon Slice : Can be eaten or pressed to get Lemon Peel;
- Sweet Peel : Mix Lemon Peel and Syrup to get this delight;
- Lemon Cake : Such as the famous Blaze Cake, the lemon cake on the other side is farmable. First craft a Cake base, then fill it with the delicious Lemonade Mocktail and Voilà;
Lemon Tree : This is where lemons comes from. Right click on leaves to get lemons.
There's more to come. 
